OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mix of early sunshine for
OL,6,Fsome and cloudy periods for others,
OL,7,Fsunshine turning hazy from late
OL,8,Fmorning and clouding over further in
OL,9,Fthe afternoon. Feeling warm, although
OL,10,Fthe breeze in places will take the
OL,11,Fedge of the temperatures.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRemaining dry with cloud
OL,14,Fclearing. The wind easing light for
OL,15,Fmost places. A mild night in urban
OL,16,Fareas but notably cooler in rural
OL,17,Fplaces.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
