OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA bright and sunny day with
OL,6,Fonly some patchy cloud in the morning
OL,7,Ffor some. Feeling warm or very warm in
OL,8,Fplaces with temperatures on the rise.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FSunny
OL,11,Fand warm for most, hot for some on
OL,12,FMonday. Expecting temperatures to
OL,13,Fdecrease Tuesday and Wednesday but
OL,14,Fremaining above average for the time
OL,15,Fof year.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
